# Library JavaScript

Reference: `src/shutters-core.js` — **vanilla JS only** (see `vanilla-js-only.mdc`).

## Class structure

- Private helpers prefixed `_` (e.g. `_toggle`, `_setState`, `_emit`)
- Public API: `open`, `close`, `toggle`, `openAll`, `closeAll`, `on`, `off`, `destroy`
- Custom events: `shutters:open`, `shutters:close` on container with `detail: { header, item }`
- Index `_byIndex()` flattens headers across all managed containers in DOM order

## Adding a public method checklist

- [ ] Implement in `src/shutters-core.js` with JSDoc
- [ ] Copy `src/shutters-core.js` → `demo/shutters-core.js`
- [ ] Document in root `README.md` API section
- [ ] Add `CHANGELOG.md` entry
- [ ] `npm run build` — verify bundle size
- [ ] `npm run agent:sync`

## Gotchas

- `open()` calls `_closeOthers` when container has `shutters-autoclose`
- `destroy()` must remove listeners AND inline CSS custom properties on containers
- Constructor throws if no containers match selector
